                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dragon launches hundreds of exploding runes that detonate upon impact, dealing @Damage[20d6[untyped]|options:area-damage] damage in a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] (@Check[reflex|dc:46|basic] save). The damage type of this ability is determined by Shifting Rune. Creatures that take damage from the breath also gain a detonating rune. The dragon can't use Runic Breath again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Runic Breath]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
